name: Hellowicked 01: Chuckie Bill
description:
Before Krowbar drop his live video set, he will drop a batch of his NFT debut. Droppin daily from today until October 31st. This one is the first. Burn everything left after 24 hours.

"This year halloween fell on a weekend/ Me and geto boyz are trick-or-treating/ Robbing little kids for bags/ Till an old man got behind our ass" -"My Mind Playing Tricks on Me"

There's no other legend represent more the wickedness than the almighty Bushwick Bill for the very first piece of Krowbar Hellowicked Season. If you know, you know. It would be a disrespect for Bill if we have to tell you who he is.
